7.5" FANTASMA MERMICORNO - One special night, a group of Unicornos were flying in the direction of falling stars. The falling stars were disappearing into a sparkly sea which transformed them into star fishes, while changing snowflakes into jelly fish. They rode the tail of a shooting star into the magical sea, turning them into enchanting creatures of half Unicorno and half fish.
